DESCRIPTION:<p>Opening Day 2026:<br>Saturday\, May 9\, 2026<br>8:30am–1:30p
 m<br>Millennium Plaza Park</p><p>Discover the region’s finest agricultural 
 and food products at the Lake Oswego Farmers’ Market. Each week you’ll find
  an exceptional selection of fresh produce\, meats\, seafood\, cheeses\, nu
 ts\, artisan breads and pastries\, jams\, salsas\, hummus\, hot foods\, nur
 sery items\, artisan crafts\, and more. There truly is something for everyo
 ne!</p><p>Enjoy live music from 10:30am–12:30pm\, engage your little ones w
 ith our Farm Fresh Kids Program\, and take advantage of our SNAP matching p
 rogram (up to $20 each week).<br><br><a href="https://www.ci.oswego.or.us/l
 ofm">https://www.ci.oswego.or.us/lofm</a></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260319T195124Z
